# Architecture

- Webhook handlers respond quickly; long-running AI work runs in background jobs.
- Keep Telegram API, Git CLI, subprocess, and AI CLI details behind adapters/services.
- Use Strategy/Factory for runner selection, Command for Telegram handlers, Facade for job orchestration — only when variability or complexity already exists.
- Do not create multiple classes for simple or single-use behavior.
- Code and tests are the source of truth for directory layout; do not maintain a file tree in docs.
